Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:17.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}随性挑选着五彩的光线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.53,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了协调我们的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:23.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}做自己想做的事情吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好热 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:01:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是夏天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是夏天了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是夏天了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么如此不必要地强调夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  我们去海边吧  去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我们下周日去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？千秋想去才去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊  你们俩都说想去才…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对了  得把泳衣找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来是有阵子没拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找着了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋找着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点儿小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（紧）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为长高了才穿不上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  绝不是变胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「成长了」这么便利的字眼是我们的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我去买新的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而春香准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？那我的泳衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心  我们会替你挑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两截儿的泳衣就不存在这种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们根本没胖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来春香的不仅是上下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右也分开比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣料分作两块…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但用线系着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让春香姐姐在大庭广众之下穿成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  你太嫰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为一名女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的裸露都没有反而不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都穿得很暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就春香穿着宇航员般厚重的潜水服跳进大海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着大家会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你要潜多深？」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让春香丢人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有替她选一款不至于丢人的布料较少的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最接近女高中生的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的饭菜也非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗茶淡饭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该让我看看你买的是怎样的泳衣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你期待那一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您别这样～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能硬来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  别发出些奇怪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让春香姐姐丢人  我们选得很卖力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会让可爱妹妹的努力白费吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨声真动听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  您说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛荡涤着我们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  这雨下几天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  三天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  已经三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来明天就是周日的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就去不成海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你还说什么「荡涤灵魂」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏这雨现在才这么凉爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来的目的也算达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种目的现在已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去海边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着雨声平静地度日也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  闭上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聆听自然那优美的歌声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不停连混凝土都得泡烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  雨云
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐正犯愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让太阳出来  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  来做晴天娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才在嘲笑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  情不自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我用床单把你给卷起来吊着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  有本事你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宫同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  放我下来  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的天气就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？难道春香姐姐乐在其中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天不放晴不会放你下来的  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（交涉）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨云先生  雨云先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  请一边凉快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像雨变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惹怒雨云怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更尊重些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:40.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（交涉Ⅱ）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨云先生  拜您所赐  大地已经得到了充分的滋润
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您差不多请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（交涉Ⅲ）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:09:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一连工作三天三夜一定累了吧  雨云大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防止水份不足  您稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太神了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨过天晴真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能去海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回再下雨就有劳你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是个晴天  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是多亏了千秋的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到客厅稍等一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于可以出发去海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放我下来  我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨云别再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  看你都做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨云先生  十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人讨厌您的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都非常喜欢您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到海边啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太平洋算什么  我们游个遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这想做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你问得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我们替你选了件布料少的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你裹那么严实做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不正为这个犯难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在千秋面上好歹是穿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心理准备还是必要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你快点来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  你很拿手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付诸武力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想使蛮的也白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又加了一件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  谁是敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道她为什么不脱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次换我来跟她谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来到海边  我们一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  请慢慢考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么着她得想到天黑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  咱俩比比谁能让她把外套脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北风和太阳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：语出《伊索寓言》）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（太阳）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（北风）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这反而让她很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那样也好不到哪儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么之后只好用水泼她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一来  她也就会投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  这样只会让她生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回她们又打的什么鬼主意…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  果然是春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希  淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学姐也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是跟社团一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那边打沙滩排球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香要参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我跟妹妹们一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很大胆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就显得我自我意识过剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不脱反而很怪的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直目不转睛地盯着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就算是顽固分子的春香也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那待会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  大家一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丰满
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丰满啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然  春香姐姐当然厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  大家快来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么让春香脱掉外套的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  茶都喝光了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我去买些冷饮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这是做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话能让你妨碍我和春香姐姐一起去购物  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脚底粘的沙子在我脸上擦着好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然觉得在你们间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的价值似乎降低了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就因为我没能让春香脱掉外套而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这个无关
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你在我心中的价值依然在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行时？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在降到哪儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还差不多是这个水准
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在得是那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Beach Sandal{\r}\N拖鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的价值就和一只丢弃的拖鞋一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要挽回名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田和吉野的家人既然把她们交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们当然就得负责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是溺水了之类就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就准备了这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样无论何时都能救她们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的价值是无限的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限的是你那蠢脑瓜子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以溺水为前提？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说这可是我的救生圈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上回是晴天娃娃  这回又让我扮作海怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:38.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：原文“海坊主”，也可解作海龟）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么着能得到什么恩惠？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  海怪是个什么视觉效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野和内田若是溺水的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可得抓紧她们别松开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你们一伙儿全拉上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想钓鱼就乘渔船去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  你滚一边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,套上这被丢弃的拖鞋滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这不是千秋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香和夏奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许说得过了些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？夏奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈真是的  居然丢下千秋一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀嗬～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我找着了这么大的贝壳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起海怪倒更像是河童的脑袋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在海里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回河里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算哪门子的挽回名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这猪头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是吉野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然从海边回来被晒得通红  火辣辣地疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晒得通红的人将来会秃顶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话一点根据也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就觉得千秋和姐姐们性格不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于明天家政课…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们会不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要都像你那样就了不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓一触即发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是大家都像我一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好悠闲～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会变成没用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是南家老二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是内田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从海边回来后我脱了很多皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱太多皮的话会变矮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别信  我家老二是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋家真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一位有趣的姐姐和一位温柔的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎每天都很愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  关于明天体育课…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着刚才的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为大家性格不同才那么愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就非常喜欢性格不同的你们俩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  来吃点心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  也算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么笨蛋会无缘无故那么兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  阿珍诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  阿珍是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道就瞎叫唤吗  蠢货
